name: Battle.net-switcher
body:
# Battle.net Switcher
Have multiple Battle.net accounts? Are you a streamer who can't be stream-sniped or just a hardcore player who wants a challenge by smurfing and climbing the ladder more time than once? Then this program will aid you with switching between different accounts.
